do_confirm_sale

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
do_confirm_sale -  This method will ask the person to confirm the sale.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void do_confirm_sale(int value,
string name,
object * sellables)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^value%^RESET%^ - the value of the thing being sold
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name the thing is sold for
%^BOLD%^sellables%^RESET%^ - the things to sell

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/inherit/craft_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method will ask the person to confirm the sale.  It will check
the extra_sell_check function and then call the extra sale thing.
.EP

